OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,4,
OL,5,FThe format of the programme - revised
OL,6,Flast year when dual presentation from
OL,7,Fboth Glasgow and Edinburgh ended -
OL,8,Fremains the same.
OL,10,FThe advantage of the new set is that it
OL,11,Flooks more modern and allows more space
OL,12,Ffor reporters to join the presenter.
OL,14,FBut I bet 90% of viewers will hardly
OL,15,Fnotice the changes in a couple of
OL,16,Fweeks. And this is how it should be.
OL,18,FThe days when regional news programmes
OL,19,Fgot brand new looks every two or three
OL,20,Fyears are thankfully gone.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
