OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,4,
OL,5,FNew looks always brought complaints -
OL,6,Fsome viewers simply disliked the
OL,7,Funfamiliarity.
OL,9,FThe STV News at 6 is a successful
OL,10,Fprogramme. The challenge was to build a
OL,11,Fnew set, refresh the graphics and
OL,12,Fpotentially enhance the programme
OL,13,Fwithout annoying loyal viewers.
OL,15,FThere have been no changes to the
OL,16,Fformat.
OL,18,FI mentioned how many regional news
OL,19,Fprogrammes used to get new looks more
OL,20,Foften than weather presenters changed
OL,21,Ftheir hairstyle.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
